\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}2 large {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/navel-orange/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 navel oranges}}, zested and juiced\
